{"tid":811710,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"買全片幅無反相機之前要三思！","createTime":"2018-09-09T05:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T08:58:10.000Z","uid":40445,"like":38,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ab408682cdf8f4b373336a4dc18e3a6a24805b30","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_6cf9775fae2ffd3e8a8c21a23ac624ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_6cf9775fae2ffd3e8a8c21a23ac624ed.jpg&h=7fb31b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_b06199400cfeda9f90ee4558df1cea34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_b06199400cfeda9f90ee4558df1cea34.jpg&h=a3410003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_77e45d349edc4275e91ac0c8f6222d6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_77e45d349edc4275e91ac0c8f6222d6c.jpg&h=1ec9b635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_1439376cdd373a469db6562f76297b2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_1439376cdd373a469db6562f76297b2b.jpg&h=b056c1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_9d92493133dd5a476fdfa423029aee62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_9d92493133dd5a476fdfa423029aee62.jpg&h=9ec7cb6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/130821_d6784c0e1c55b415443d199ff6438ef9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F130821_d6784c0e1c55b415443d199ff6438ef9.jpg&h=8654d14f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c21f9f8347ecdde5b0d96db34465af38c8f9570","tid":811710,"uid":6848,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"世界大戰抹黑宇宙"},{"pid":"8b3217a7bf08c60235846d16de8e56b95ee87288","tid":811710,"uid":50502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"old news is so exciting"},{"pid":"d2553ec14ab2d236f3f8b216554bd9cf94d7c652","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全片幅無反是否全面勝過單反呢？大家都知道答案是否定的，在打算選購全片幅無反相機時，不妨「停一停，諗一諗」</span>"},{"pid":"307a326c995bd760ffd90aaf7c513b5263e1d9a4","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知道，無反相機減省了反光鏡結構，因此機身體積也得以縮小。不過不要忘記無論是單反抑或是無反，只要片幅一樣，鏡頭的重量及體積也不會相差太遠。反而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無反的重量較為集中於鏡頭，在頭重尾輕的情況下，為避免鏡頭方向墜下，握機的手指力度反而要更大。</span>"},{"pid":"ee93aed90eb4b1b1522ee5d5924f41ba1a642bda","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"如果大家的拍攝量較大，就絕對不能忽視耗電量的問題。比較一下現時同級的全片幅無反及單反，使用一枚電池，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">單反最多可以拍 1000 張，而不論什麼無反都是三百張左右。</span>電量相差足有一倍，而拍攝張數相差更多。所以如果需要拍攝同樣數量的相片，現時全片幅無反就要多帶一倍數量的電池，重量就自然有所增加，而且電池充電次數倍增，理論上也會令電池壽命減半，在購買電池上就會有較多的花費。"},{"pid":"a5d313bcf668bb18bd5a67dc575e25d36805a70a","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"現時的全片幅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">單反已經有完善的自家鏡頭系統</span>，以 Canon 為例，現役原廠全片幅鏡頭接近 60 支，當中包括魚眼鏡、微距鏡、移軸鏡、超遠攝鏡頭等，選擇方面更為齊備。而且由於機身可因應鏡頭的特點而進行機內優化，畫質方面就更令人放心。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無反原廠鏡頭5隻手指數得哂！</span>"},{"pid":"01b511df77b69c33dbf6a96562dad98c80f7c18a","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EVF 最大的缺點，就是有時滯的問題。</span>我們習慣了使用光學觀景器 OVF 取景，觀景窗裡的畫面就是主體即時的情況，光學取景是沒有遲滯的，反應也更加直接。反而使用 EVF 或 LCD 取景時，由於畫面要經過處理，所以或多或少都會有一點 delay，當大家看到這畫面再接下快門時，其實這個畫面已經過去了，對於拍攝運動、小孩、擺鏡方式之類較著重反應的題材時，攝影師可能會更為吃力。<br />\n<br />\n 由於單反相機在拍攝時，需要升起反光鏡，所以 OVF 在曝光時會有短暫的遮黑時間。不過大家不要以為用 EVF 就沒有遮黑，無反相機也是使用機械快門來控制曝光的，當曝光完成快門後簾關上時，EVF 也會有不短的遮黑時間。反而在連拍的時候，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無反相機受 EVF 取景時滯加上遮黑影響，取景畫面還遠不及 OVF 清晰流暢。</span>"},{"pid":"478c7254f7d09e18f42da0cf39ca1cb5dda4603a","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"大家也要考慮一下相機的起動時間。使用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全片幅單反，由於 OVF 觀景器不需要時間啟動</span>，所以無論是由關機至開機，或者在 sleep mode 按半下快門喚醒相機，都可以在極短時間內完成。<br />\n<br />\n反而使用全片幅無反相機，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EVF 始終需要時間啟動</span>，所以開機及喚醒相機要待一會才會顯示畫面。對於拍攝靜物來說，這些等候時間可能是無關痛癢的。但突發的情景往往在大家意料不到時發生，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">生活中精彩的一刻往往在你等開機時溜走</span>，這實在是太過可惜了。"},{"pid":"143621cb13c36856aaa0d1b5c22e1decb56e3f7a","tid":811710,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> old news is..."},{"pid":"ec6999d0515e5598bb4810ca30819ac70eb16201","tid":811710,"uid":9315,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔貼link就以為冇人知你篇野3年前?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=14261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D14261&d=KhwCWPVkS6KQF36Z2BkHHxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=01545067\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=14261</a><br />\n考古好好玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75567a3f612328c27c1fcd9db5dbe7da967b14c6","tid":811710,"uid":40445,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e